<item>
            <title>[LU-2219] so_hpreq_handler is set twice for the ost_io service</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2219</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ptlrpc_service_conf.psc_ops.so_hpreq_handler is set twice for the ost_io service in ost_setup(); the second assignment overwrites the first to NULL, so ost_io threads would never handle RPCs as high-priority ones&lt;/p&gt;</description>
